{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Shoji, Shocking, SHOJING. <br>Break through, instinctively.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/20241016_Run_600.gif?t=1729922957\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> &quot;SHOJING&quot; is a casual game in which you control a cat and break shoji screens.  <br>Why not try breaking down those shoji screens to your heart's content, something that you're not allowed to break in the real world? <br>Good children and good cats, please do not copy this game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/\u3057\u306e\u3076\u3068\u30cd\u30b3.gif?t=1729922957\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Operation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy operation with only mouse movement and left click. <br>Even those who do not usually play games and children can easily play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/20241016_Choru_600.gif?t=1729922957\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sound</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cats jump and break shoji screens to the rhythm of the background music.<br>As you connect combos, the background music and game speed increase, and the exhilaration increases!<br>Get into the rhythm and break the shoji screens as fast as you can!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Challenge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The controls are easy to use, but the game requires serious maneuvering in order to achieve the perfect shoji-breaking.<br>Connect combos, avoid obstacles, and aim for a high score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171930/extras/SHOJING_240816_\u30e1\u30cb\u30e5\u30fc.gif?t=1729922957\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamst